'''拖网捕鱼'''是[[渔船|渔船]][[捕鱼|捕鱼]]的一种方法。这种捕鱼工具被用于捞取[[扇贝|扇贝]]、[[牡蛎|牡蛎]]和其他[[蛤|蛤类]]，同时也可以用于采集[[海洋|海洋]]中[[海底|海底]][[沉积物|沉积物]]样本。<ref name=Moore>Moore G., Jennings S. & Croxall J. (2000) [http://books.google.co.nz/books?id=HX6AV1hyM20C&pg=PA14&lpg=PA14&dq=%22scallop+dredge%22+-nz&source=web&ots=Hl_HKma3tG&sig=pXkXlc5nouinQYLFJtipHSKMhBQ&hl=en#PPA14,M1 ''Commercial Fishing: The Wider Ecological Impacts.''] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.co.nz/books?id=HX6AV1hyM20C&pg=PA14&lpg=PA14&dq=%22scallop+dredge%22+-nz&source=web&ots=Hl_HKma3tG&sig=pXkXlc5nouinQYLFJtipHSKMhBQ&hl=en#PPA14,M1 |date=20191130031401 }} British Ecological Society. ISBN 0-632-05608-8. Page 14</ref> 

==结构==
拖网捕鱼使用一个很重的捞取工具，由[[钢铁|钢铁]]框架制作，框架的前端有一根链条[[网丝|网丝]]（又称拖曳缆绳），用于拖曳，还有一个底栖拖网。框架可以安装一根棒子在尾部。<ref>[http://www.seafish.org/upload/b2b/file/r__d/DREDGES_9.pdf Dredges] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090326130854/http://www.seafish.org/upload/b2b/file/r__d/DREDGES_9.pdf |date=2009-03-26 }} seafood.org. Retrieved 11 February 2009.</ref>

==影響==
部分拖網方式，例如{{link-en|底拖網|bottom trawling}}，對環境影響很大，某些地區例如香港已立法禁止。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/publications/publications_press/pr1816.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2019-11-29 |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130203224/https://www.afcd.gov.hk/tc_chi/publications/publications_press/pr1816.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

